Bundled fonts and their licenses
=================================

This directory bundles two fonts used to render Stream Deck button images.
Both are permissively licensed (MIT-compatible).

  lucide.ttf      Lucide icon font           ISC License + MIT (Feather subset)
  DejaVuSans.ttf  DejaVu Sans (button text)  Bitstream Vera + Arev licenses


